Package crazyballrun.game.level.objects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LevelObject
    This abstract class defines basic functionality of static and moving objects in a level.
    LevelObjectFactory
    The LevelObjectFactory generates instances of different LevelObject- implementations.
    LevelObjectParser
    The LevelObjectParser reads an XML-file and extracts all necessary information from it to create a valid instance LevelObject.
    SimpleCar
    SimpleCar is a LevelObject-implementation of a simple car (like the name says).
    SimpleRocket
    The SimpleRocket is an easy implementation of LevelObject that produces a strange rotation-effect uppon another object when colliding.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    LevelObject.ObjectState
    All possible state of a level object.
